\begin_layout Standard
The milk analyzers were delivered with clear Standard Operating Procedures.
 Two separate trainings were organized.
 One training targeted MCC owners,
 where the focus was mostly on generating buy-in by pointing out the benefits of measuring and tracking milk quality.
 A second training was geared toward MCC managers and focused more on use and maintenance of the milk analyzers.
