\begin_layout Standard
We collaborated with the DDA to set up a system to monitor the milk analyzers and its use.
 In particular,
 DDA technicians visited treatment MCCs at set periods.
 We also provided various ways in which MCC managers could request assistance if needed,
 including a WhatAapp group and a telephone hotline.
 We also made sure that,
